{"tid":2010263,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"區議員籲母親節霸枱淨飲","createTime":"2020-05-10T10:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T10:00:24.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c079fd19ca967b546c710abf2dca6171d289626","tid":2010263,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200510/_2020051009574689326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200510%2F_2020051009574689326.jpg&h=37d52170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊彧。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n本地疫情緩和，上周五（五月八日）起放寬限聚令的食肆每枱人數，由四人增至八人，正好趕及母親節。本港飲食業早前受疫情影響生意大跌，希望藉今個母親節，能吸引多些顧客，但深水埗區議員的楊彧昨日卻在其臉書專頁帖文，呼籲市民在今日母親節「支持美孚富臨大行動」，於今早十一時起「和你淨飲茶」，更要一人一張枱。<br />\n<br />\n楊議員聲稱富臨可以獲得政府推出的一億七千萬抗疫基金的資助，但員工放兩個月無薪假，於是便在facebook專頁內，表明富臨可能最近生意差，所以「我哋一齊趁母親節，去畀啲支持畀美孚富臨好唔好？淨飲的話，杯茶會貴少少，希望可以畀到多啲支持畀富臨出糧畀員工」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1767370/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%8A%E6%90%9E%E5%B1%80-%E7%B1%B2%E9%9C%B8%E6%9E%B1-%E6%B7%A8%E9%A3%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1767370%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%259E%25B1-%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E9%25A3%25B2&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=d0514c11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1767370%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%259E%25B1-%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E9%25A3%25B2&h=54f41aed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1767370/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%8A%E6%90%9E%E5%B1%80-%E7%B1%B2%E9%9C%B8%E6%9E%B1-%E6%B7%A8%E9%A3%B2</a>"},{"pid":"b219f812d27ac11258c12d0f0f87711055991839","tid":2010263,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"此post 已完 多謝"}]}